Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:19.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:27.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:32.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 看起來心事很重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:37.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們到底是是不被歡迎呢 氣氛好沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天居然被那麼正式地否定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:34.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}拒絕色的烹飪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個氛圍的中心 就是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}成績優秀 認真 有威信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是結女的代表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且聽說還是學園理事長的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:04.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的人物拒絕合併的話 對結女的其他人也會產生影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少我是不歡迎你們男生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這個結姬女子學園是女校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:21.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說 能夠改變這樣氣氛的關鍵也是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:32.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:38.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要能溝通的話 還是需要些時間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:04:00.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看起來一副忐忑不安的樣子呢 新吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔在教室也是女僕裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 安潔從母親那代開始就是女僕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順便說一句 母親是英國人 所以我是混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:22.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長承認的野生女僕是同班同學的事雖然還沒能適應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:27.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 最重要的還是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的邂逅就像夢境一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:53.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}糟糕 我到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒注意 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生請使用男生臨時洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 接下來是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:46.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來就是少女的花園 所以沒料到會有男生在這裡學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生更衣室也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在庭院的偏僻處換衣服可是很痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:59.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是這種時候 作為學生會會長的你更應該做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:05.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說 我還有各務台的工作要做 很忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:09.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兩個人好像都沒有能放鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:10.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該說 為什麼是體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很遺憾沒有女僕用的體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是安潔一直都是女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:25.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以給大家帶來了慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:30.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽說燒水壺的水 無論大家有多麼勞累也能馬上變得有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像在什麼地方有些誤解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 謝謝你帶來的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔不反對合併學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:49.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 安潔即使學生數增多了 也不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:55.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能夠成為安潔主人的人 或許能夠增加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:07:00.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女的女生 要是都像安潔那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用那麼在意也無所謂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是乾 紗凪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:07.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然反對的人也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:17.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但也去接受了 這就是所謂的溫柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 小紗真的是好溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:24.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不… 不是那麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:29.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等我 小紗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是所有人都反對合併學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:40.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是只要她還在反對 氣氛就不會改善吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:55.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 總之就努力打開她的心結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:57.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 你可真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 這是誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:11.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}敲門一下是會怎樣阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 真的是很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:28.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經沒關係了 我已經知道瓜生是那樣的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}粉 粉筆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偷窺 聽說瓜生是首犯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了偷窺瀨名的裙子下面 故意將粉筆給…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連我們學校的女生都成為敵人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}氣氛變得更糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但這可真不像新吾一貫的作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:09.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被發現後 還在狡辯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:25.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉 好像教室裏越來越沒有容身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:31.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔 今天也努力做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起了 櫻乃

Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫我的嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 好像在哪裡看過一樣

Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我是瓜生 要吃便當嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:54.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵 在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 小熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫天羽美羽 是三年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 三年級生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:32.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫瓜生新吾 二年級生 那個各務台的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試驗班的吧 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:43.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 你好 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:49.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我從小學開始就一直是在女校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和男生說話對我很新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:57.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真好啊 一二年級有試驗生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:07.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 想到前輩歡迎我們 就很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來很好吃的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:16.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 妹妹想著 到了一個新學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好孩子 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:25.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:32.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然在適應前會很辛苦 但這是個很好的學園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生一定也會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 今後也多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天羽美羽前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這裡是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還算是歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 可能因為我也是女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這或許也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:17.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是沒關係 哥哥一直很擅長對付女性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說得我好像花花公子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這個意思 哥哥和我在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:33.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要保持哥哥平時的樣子就可以了 我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:38.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:47.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和各務台的同學們一起度過的這段時間 什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:51.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生比想象中的還要下流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有女生在的時候輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該將他們給趕出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說話也很粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做事都很小孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}評價很差啊 男生們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:10.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是試驗生來了之後 開始注重儀容的女生沒有增加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:12.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}儀容是開始注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:17.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有意識到異性的存在 這樣的地方就容易粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然作為女人生出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就該磨礪自己 成為一個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天開始 特別課程也重新進行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生 加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女生 也不要被看到弱點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是特別課程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:45.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯 不僅僅是料理 還有裁縫 茶道 花道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣必備的素質全部都有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:51.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了磨練女性的能力的特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也要磨練女性的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:13:59.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:05.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天一起做栗子飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}T組已經分好小組了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}6個人分成一個小組
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:17.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女 各務台女生 男生分別兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一下子就是和女生一起的實習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:22.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果做得不好 肯定會更加被反感了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要保持哥哥平時的樣子就可以了 我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想瓜生一定也會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之 儘量能夠不拖別人後腿 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你妨礙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:57.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剝慄子的皮真難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說交給你就可以的 是椋梨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:05.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剝慄子皮的時候 請注意菜刀的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 真熟練的手法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾 這裡準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 順利剝開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝你教我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}米還沒洗呢 我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:33.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾經常做料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是幫忙打下手的程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生也不會去妨礙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且剝皮的手法也很高超
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 只要模仿新吾就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:03.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:08.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:10.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯 不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生們也開始能幫上忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:15.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然沒有瓜生那樣的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不會輸的 新吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}堵上女僕的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:25.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔更能幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來只要等煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:40.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生和女生互相幫忙 這是一個不錯的機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 需要我幫什麼忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不需要 請不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪 把剩下的牛蒡材料給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是一點不浪費啊 愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 我們的小組連味繒湯都做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:13.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名不僅學習好 料理也很有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:18.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要先把殘渣除去 剩下的就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是那步驟卻很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那只能去適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:30.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名是那種就算沒有異性的眼光 也不會有疏漏的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做得可真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:46.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟 食材可以隨便使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說需要 安潔就一直拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可沒那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:57.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們明白的吧 特別課程做的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:00.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有全部吃掉的話 是不給成績的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:13.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我肚子餓極了 給我上最大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 拜託給我最大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再來一碗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:38.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:02.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很能幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:28.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:29.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 今天稍微有精神點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個是…

Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是謎之生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:04.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 見過一面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不久前見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:19.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試驗合校 已經過了一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:25.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}選舉班長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:25.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果能快點選舉出班長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師 老師會很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為是一個班級
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:38.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以從結女和各務台各選出一名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:46.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我pass
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該說 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:52.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且我還擔任著各務台的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:56.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這裡的學生會 也有著副會長的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:58.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:02.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是 我推薦新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:03.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:04.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:06.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:13.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾的話 能夠看清楚氣氛 把事情做好的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了  那我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會忙起來的

Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:35.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 被選舉出來的人站起來 向大家問好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 果然是新吾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 能夠接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那邊也是理所當然的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那確實是 那樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這不是開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會和那樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

